The <b>Cognitive Technology Threat Warning System</b>, otherwise known as (CT2WS), is a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../164/1164.xml">
artificial cognitive science</link> program designed to analysis sensory-data and then alert foot-soldiers to any possible threats, passive or direct.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref> CT2WS is part of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../897/7279897.xml">
U.S. Department of Defense's</link> effort to produce an efficient and working <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../505/1733505.xml">
